Phillies’ Halladay to Face Angels’ Weaver as Starting All-Star Pitchers

-- B y   E b e n   N o v y - W i l l i a m s
-- 
2011-07-11T17:06:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/phillies-halladay-to-face-angels-weaver-as-starting-all-star-pitchers.html
Roy Halladay  of the  Philadelphia
Phillies  will face Jered Weaver of the Los Angeles Angels as
starting pitchers in tomorrow’s Major League Baseball All-Star
Game, according to a post by MLB on the Twitter social network.  To contact the reporter on this story:
